extends layouts/modern-layout

block layout-content
  // Breadcrumb Navigation
  .container.mt-4
    nav(aria-label='breadcrumb')
      ol.breadcrumb
        li.breadcrumb-item
          a.text-decoration-none(href='/') Home
        li.breadcrumb-item
          a.text-decoration-none(href='/articles.html') Articles
        li.breadcrumb-item.active(aria-current='page') Trivia Spark

  // Hero Section
  section.bg-gradient-primary.py-5
    .container
      .row.align-items-center
        .col-lg-10.mx-auto.text-center
          h1.display-4.fw-bold.mb-3
            i.bi.bi-lightning-charge.me-3
            | Trivia Spark
          h2.h3.mb-4 Igniting Creativity with ChatGPT
          p.lead.mb-5
            | Follow the journey of building a trivia app with the help of ChatGPT—rapid prototyping, creative problem solving, and AI-powered development.

  // Main Article Content
  article#main-article
    .container
      .row
        .col-lg-8.mx-auto
          // Article metadata
          .article-meta.text-muted.mb-4.pb-3.border-bottom
            .row.align-items-center
              .col-md-8
                .d-flex.flex-wrap.gap-3
                  .d-flex.align-items-center
                    i.bi.bi-calendar3.me-2
                    time(datetime=modifiedDate) May 30, 2025
                  .d-flex.align-items-center
                    i.bi.bi-person.me-2
                    span by Mark Hazleton
                  .d-flex.align-items-center
                    i.bi.bi-clock.me-2
                    span= estimatedReadTime + ' min read'
              .col-md-4.text-md-end
                .d-flex.flex-wrap.gap-2.justify-content-md-end
                  span.badge.bg-primary AI
                  span.badge.bg-secondary Trivia
                  span.badge.bg-success Collaboration

          // Table of Contents
          nav#table-of-contents.mb-5(aria-label='Table of Contents')
            .card
              .card-header.bg-primary.text-white
                h3.card-title.mb-0
                  i.bi.bi-list-ul.me-2
                  | Table of Contents
              .card-body
                ol.list-group.list-group-numbered.list-group-flush
                  li.list-group-item
                    a.text-decoration-none(href='#introduction') Introduction
                  li.list-group-item
                    a.text-decoration-none(href='#collaboration') Collaboration with ChatGPT
                  li.list-group-item
                    a.text-decoration-none(href='#trusted-advisor') Chat as Trusted Advisor
                  li.list-group-item
                    a.text-decoration-none(href='#copilot') ChatGPT vs GitHub Copilot
                  li.list-group-item
                    a.text-decoration-none(href='#screenshots') Chat In Action
                  li.list-group-item
                    a.text-decoration-none(href='#conclusion') Parting Thoughts

          // Introduction
          section#introduction.mb-5
            p.lead
              | Welcome to the kickoff of the Trivia Spark application! Trivia Spark is my experiment in using ChatGPT to help develop a trivia application. This page documents the collaboration and progress as the project evolves.
            .alert.alert-info.d-flex.align-items-center.mb-4
              i.bi.bi-github.fs-4.me-3
              div
                h6.alert-heading.mb-1 Project Links
                ul.mb-0.ps-3
                  li
                    a(href='https://github.com/controlorigins/triviaspark', target='_blank', rel='noopener') Trivia Spark GitHub Repository (old)
                  li
                    a(href='https://webspark.markhazleton.com/TriviaSpark', target='_blank', rel='noopener') Trivia Spark Website
                  li
                    a(href='https://markhazleton.com/using-chatgpt-for-developers.html', target='_self') Article – Using ChatGPT for Developers
            figure.mb-4
              img.img-fluid.rounded(src='assets/img/MarkHazleton-ChatGPT-TriviaSparkMatch.png' alt='Trivia Spark Early Screenshot' loading='lazy' title='Trivia Spark Early Screenshot')
              figcaption.text-muted.mt-2.small Early Trivia Spark prototype screenshot

          // Collaboration with ChatGPT
          section#collaboration.mb-5
            h2.h3.mb-4.text-primary Collaboration with ChatGPT
            p
              | The Trivia Spark application began as an exploration of public APIs, specifically the Open Trivia Database. ChatGPT provided suggestions, code snippets, and creative solutions to overcome development challenges and accelerate prototyping.
            p
              | ChatGPT helped brainstorm approaches, debug issues, and iterate on features. Its ability to quickly generate code and offer alternative solutions made it an invaluable collaborator.
            p
              | Rapid prototyping and feedback cycles allowed for experimentation and refinement, resulting in a more robust and flexible trivia app.

          // Chat as Trusted Advisor
          section#trusted-advisor.mb-5
            h2.h3.mb-4.text-primary Chat as Trusted Advisor
            p
              | ChatGPT acted as a trusted advisor throughout the project, suggesting architectural patterns like enums and dictionaries for flexible game modes, and lazy loading for model management. Its feedback and willingness to iterate led to better design decisions and maintainable code.
            p
              | The collaboration highlighted the value of AI as a development partner—offering expertise, adapting to feedback, and accelerating progress without ego.

          // ChatGPT vs GitHub Copilot
          section#copilot.mb-5
            h2.h3.mb-4.text-primary ChatGPT vs GitHub Copilot
            p
              | Both ChatGPT and GitHub Copilot were used in developing Trivia Spark. Copilot excels at code completion and context-aware suggestions, while ChatGPT provides broader architectural advice and problem-solving support. Together, they form a powerful toolkit for modern developers.
            p
              | Copilot’s AI-driven code suggestions complement ChatGPT’s conversational guidance, enabling faster, higher-quality development.

          // Chat In Action (Screenshots)
          section#screenshots.mb-5
            h2.h3.mb-4.text-primary Chat In Action
            p
              | Here are a few screenshots illustrating the collaboration with ChatGPT during Trivia Spark’s development.
            .carousel.slide#carouselControlOrigins(data-bs-ride='carousel')
              .carousel-indicators
                button.active(type='button' data-bs-target='#carouselControlOrigins' data-bs-slide-to='0' aria-label='Slide 1')
                button(type='button' data-bs-target='#carouselControlOrigins' data-bs-slide-to='1' aria-label='Slide 2')
                button(type='button' data-bs-target='#carouselControlOrigins' data-bs-slide-to='2' aria-label='Slide 3')
                button(type='button' data-bs-target='#carouselControlOrigins' data-bs-slide-to='3' aria-label='Slide 4')
                button(type='button' data-bs-target='#carouselControlOrigins' data-bs-slide-to='4' aria-label='Slide 5')
                button(type='button' data-bs-target='#carouselControlOrigins' data-bs-slide-to='5' aria-label='Slide 6')
                button(type='button' data-bs-target='#carouselControlOrigins' data-bs-slide-to='6' aria-label='Slide 7')
                button(type='button' data-bs-target='#carouselControlOrigins' data-bs-slide-to='7' aria-label='Slide 8')
                button(type='button' data-bs-target='#carouselControlOrigins' data-bs-slide-to='8' aria-label='Slide 9')
              .carousel-inner
                .carousel-item.active
                  .container.text-center
                    h5 Get Unanswered Questions
                    img.img-fluid.rounded.mx-auto.d-block(src='assets/img/MarkHazleton-ChatGPT-GetUnAnsweredQuestions.png' alt='Get Unanswered Questions' loading='lazy')
                .carousel-item
                  .container.text-center
                    h5 Lazy Loading Example
                    img.img-fluid.rounded.mx-auto.d-block(src='assets/img/MarkHazleton-ChatGPT-LazyLoadingExample.png' alt='Lazy Loading Example' loading='lazy')
                .carousel-item
                  .container.text-center
                    h5 Pros and Cons of Virtual Methods
                    img.img-fluid.rounded.mx-auto.d-block(src='assets/img/MarkHazleton-ChatGPT-ProConVirtualMethods.png' alt='Pros and Cons of Virtual Methods' loading='lazy')
                .carousel-item
                  .container.text-center
                    h5 Refactor With Suggestions
                    img.img-fluid.rounded.mx-auto.d-block(src='assets/img/MarkHazleton-ChatGPT-RefactorWithInput.png' alt='Refactor With Suggestions' loading='lazy')
                .carousel-item
                  .container.text-center
                    h5 Optimize With Hashset
                    img.img-fluid.rounded.mx-auto.d-block(src='assets/img/MarkHazleton-ChatGPT-OptimizeWithHashSet.png' alt='Optimize With Hashset' loading='lazy')
                .carousel-item
                  .container.text-center
                    h5 Rapid Prototyping
                    img.img-fluid.rounded.mx-auto.d-block(src='assets/img/MarkHazleton-ChatGPT-RapidPrototyping.png' alt='Rapid Prototyping' loading='lazy')
                .carousel-item
                  .container.text-center
                    h5 Get Incorrect Questions
                    img.img-fluid.rounded.mx-auto.d-block(src='assets/img/MarkHazleton-ChatGPT-GetIncorrectQuestions.png' alt='Get Incorrect Questions' loading='lazy')
                .carousel-item
                  .container.text-center
                    h5 Game Play Modes
                    img.img-fluid.rounded.mx-auto.d-block(src='assets/img/MarkHazleton-ChatGPT-GamePlayModes.png' alt='Game Play Modes' loading='lazy')
                .carousel-item
                  .container.text-center
                    h5 ENUM Parse from String
                    img.img-fluid.rounded.mx-auto.d-block(src='assets/img/MarkHazleton-ChatGPT-EnumParse.png' alt='Enum Parse from String' loading='lazy')
              button.carousel-control-prev(type='button' data-bs-target='#carouselControlOrigins' data-bs-slide='prev')
                span.carousel-control-prev-icon(aria-hidden='true')
                span.visually-hidden Previous
              button.carousel-control-next(type='button' data-bs-target='#carouselControlOrigins' data-bs-slide='next')
                span.carousel-control-next-icon(aria-hidden='true')
                span.visually-hidden Next

          // Conclusion
          section#conclusion.mb-5
            h2.h3.mb-4.text-primary Parting Thoughts
            .key-takeaway.mb-4
              h4.h5.mb-3
                i.bi.bi-lightbulb.me-2
                | Key Takeaways
              ul.list-unstyled
                li.mb-2
                  | Collaboration with ChatGPT enabled rapid prototyping and creative problem solving.
                li.mb-2
                  | Combining ChatGPT and GitHub Copilot accelerates development and improves code quality.
                li.mb-2
                  | AI tools are valuable partners for modern software development.
            p
              | The kickoff of the Trivia Spark application was a collaborative effort with ChatGPT. Working with AI enabled quick prototyping, overcoming obstacles, and building a working app in a short time.
            p
              | Collaboration between humans and AI models like ChatGPT is becoming increasingly common in software development. The tools I use are constantly evolving, and I continue to evaluate new ways to improve my process.
            p
              | Here are a few of the other tools and reference sources I use:
            ul
              li
                a(href='https://visualstudio.microsoft.com/vs/', target='_blank', rel='noopener') Visual Studio 2022
              li
                a(href='https://www.devexpress.com/products/coderush/', target='_blank', rel='noopener') Coderush by DevExpress
              li
                a(href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/GitHub_Copilot', target='_blank', rel='noopener') GitHub Copilot
              li
                a(href='https://stackoverflow.com/', target='_blank', rel='noopener') Stack Overflow
              li
                a(href='https://www.dotnetrocks.com/', target='_blank', rel='noopener') .NET Rocks
              li
                a(href='https://wilderminds.com/', target='_blank', rel='noopener') Shawn Wildermuth – Wilder Minds
              li
                a(href='https://www.hanselman.com/', target='_blank', rel='noopener') Scott Hanselman
              li
                a(href='https://nickchapsas.com/', target='_blank', rel='noopener') Nick Chapsas – Keep Coding
  hr.m-0
